snippet.title: Slipgate Demo - "Blood and Gibs" Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore a gloomy rooms of damned sci-fi base as a Jack "Hammer" Thompson - a doomed marine, only survivor of the portal experiment. Save humanity like in 90's with your trusty shotgun!

Play demo today: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2204910/Slipgate/
Join Discord: https://discord.gg/n9T8MFZVfD
#slipgate #doom #fps #indie #gamedev
